Benefits

Helps in premature greying
Promotes thicker, faster hair growth
Deeply nourishes scalp & prevents dryness
Adds shine and smoothness
Reduces dandruff and scalp irritation
Improves blood circulation to the scalp
Reduces hair fall and strengthens roots

Ingredients:

Coconut Oil
Olive Oil
Almond Oil
Black Sesame Oil
Castor Oil
Rosemary Extract
Vitamin-E
Amla
Reetha
Brahmi
Shikakai
Hibiscus
Fenugreek
Bhringraj
Kalonji
Jatamasi

How to Use

Take a small amount of oil.
Gently massage onto scalp for 3–5 minutes.
Leave it Full Day or Overnight or at least 2 hour.
Use 3–4 times a week for best results.

Caution

For external use only
Avoid contact with eyes
Keep away from children
If irritation occurs, discontinue use
Store in a cool & dry place
